Dataset and Code Use Notice

Copyright (c) 2026 Muhammad Ali Azam Khattak

This repository contains two types of material:

1. Documentation and code files
2. Dataset files derived from multilingual offensive-language resources

Documentation and code files may be used for research and educational purposes with attribution.

Dataset files are provided for research, education, benchmark evaluation, and moderation-support experiments only. Because the dataset may include material derived from multiple original resources and social media text, users must check and respect the licences, permissions, and terms of use of the original sources before redistribution, commercial use, or public deployment.

Users are not permitted to use this dataset to:
- target, harass, profile, or discriminate against individuals or communities;
- generate or amplify hateful, abusive, or harmful content;
- claim that the dataset represents all speakers of any language or community;
- deploy automated moderation systems without appropriate human review and bias assessment.

When using this resource, users should cite the associated paper and repository citation metadata.

IMPORTANT:
If the original source datasets use specific licences, those licences take precedence for the relevant portions of the data. This notice should be replaced or updated with a formal licence after all original source dataset licences and redistribution rights have been verified.
